{"words":[{"word":"sorry","count":3},{"word":"return","count":3},{"word":"rite","count":3},{"word":"soliskin","count":3},{"word":"yes","count":2},{"word":"deeply","count":2},{"word":"academy","count":2},{"word":"impossible","count":2},{"word":"ano","count":2},{"word":"te","count":2},{"word":"attend","count":2},{"word":"roya","count":2},{"word":"saved","count":2},{"word":"hm","count":1},{"word":"greetings","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"home","count":1},{"word":"visit","count":1},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"broken","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"school","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"h-how","count":1},{"word":"taught","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"whatever","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"offer","count":1},{"word":"apologies","count":1},{"word":"behalf","count":1},{"word":"punishment","count":1},{"word":"severe","count":1},{"word":"compensation","count":1},{"word":"needed","count":1},{"word":"pay","count":1},{"word":"voidmatter","count":1},{"word":"exactly","count":1},{"word":"asking","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"studied","count":1},{"word":"startorch","count":1},{"word":"familiar","count":1},{"word":"terms","count":1},{"word":"n-no","count":1},{"word":"robots'","count":1},{"word":"path","count":1},{"word":"traced","count":1},{"word":"expose","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"maja","count":1},{"word":"activate","count":1},{"word":"robots","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"exact","count":1},{"word":"location","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"solsworn","count":1},{"word":"successors","count":1},{"word":"chosen","count":1},{"word":"resonance","count":1},{"word":"ability","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"awakens","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"desired","count":1},{"word":"position","count":1},{"word":"change","count":1},{"word":"appointment","count":1},{"word":"solisylum's","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"usually","count":1},{"word":"abide","count":1},{"word":"village","count":1},{"word":"bordering","count":1},{"word":"bjartr","count":1},{"word":"woods","count":1},{"word":"called","count":1},{"word":"haldarheim","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"href","count":1},{"word":"solistrees","count":1},{"word":"exostrider","count":1},{"word":"tradition","count":1},{"word":"foreseer","count":1},{"word":"yngvar","count":1},{"word":"allowed","count":1},{"word":"witness","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"shepherds","count":1},{"word":"companions","count":1},{"word":"hundreds","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"hear","count":1},{"word":"grateful","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hm? Greetings. Yes, I am. And you two are?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"A home visit...? Has the girl broken any school rules?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"What?! H-How could she...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I am deeply sorry! I should have taught her better. Whatever she has done, I offer my apologies to the Academy on her behalf.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Is the punishment severe? If compensation is needed, I will pay for it myself—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Voidmatter?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"What... exactly are you asking? I am sorry, I've not studied at your Startorch Academy. I'm not familiar with your terms.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"N-No. We can't. If the robots' path is traced, it will expose that thing—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I am deeply sorry! Yes, help Maja activate the robots I did, but I... I can't remember the exact location. Please, you must return—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"No. That is impossible.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Each of <ano=the Solsworn>these successors</ano> is chosen when their Resonance Ability first awakens. Even if someone desired the position, it is impossible to change the appointment.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"The Solisylum's people usually abide in the village bordering Bjartr Woods, called Haldarheim.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"It is the time of the <te href=700028>Rite of Return</te>. The Soliskin will return to the Solistrees and to the Exostrider. As is tradition, Foreseer Yngvar will attend the rite.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"But you are not Roya. You may not be allowed to witness the rite.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Is this the Soliskin you saved? Well... Perhaps you may attend as \"Shepherds.\"","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Soliskin have been companions to the Roya for hundreds of years. If they hear that you saved one, they will be grateful.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002}]}